#: ../main.lua:654
msgid   "Usage Tips\n"
        "\n"
        "Select:\n"
        "Highlight text (or a word) in the book, then press [AI assistant] in the poped up menu.\n"
        "\n"
        "Long Press:\n"
        "- On a Prompt Button: Add to the highlight menu.\n"
        "- On a highlight menu button to remove it.\n"
        "- On the Close button to go back to the book in 1 step.\n"
        "\n"
        "Very-Long Press (over 3 seconds):\n"
        "On a single word in the book to show the highlight menu (instead of the dictionary).\n"
        "\n"
        "Multi-Swipe (e.g., ⮠, ⮡, ↺):\n"
        "On the result dialog to close (as the Close button is far to reach).\n"
msgstr  "Sarrerako aholkuak\n"
        "\n"
        "Aukeratu:\n"
        "Altzarpiten testua (edo hizkia) liburuan, ondoren [AI laguntzailea] sakatu apagailutako menuan.\n"
        "\n"
        "Sakatu luzea:\n"
        "- Prompt Botoian: Gehitu altzarpakiko menuan.\n"
        "- Altzarpakiko menu botoi batean ezabatu.\n"
        "- Itxi botoian itzuli liburua batera.\n"
        "\n"
        "Saihotxoan Sakatu (3 segundo baino gehiago):\n"
        "Liburuko hizkia altzarapen menua erakusten ditu (hiztegiaren ordez).\n"
        "\n"
        "Multi-Eskaia (nola: ⮠, ⮡, ↺):\n"
        "Erantzuneko elkarteetan itxi (Itxi botoia aholku ezinezkoa den kasutan).\n"

